Module java.money
Package javax.money.format

Class AmountFormatContextBuilder

java.lang.Object
javax.money.AbstractContextBuilder<AmountFormatContextBuilder,​AmountFormatContext>
javax.money.format.AmountFormatContextBuilder
public final class AmountFormatContextBuilder
extends AbstractContextBuilder<AmountFormatContextBuilder,​AmountFormatContext>
Builder class for creating new instances of AmountFormatContext adding detailed information about a MonetaryAmountFormat instance.

Note this class is NOT thread-safe.

See Also:
MonetaryAmountFormat.getContext()
